todomato

Class Task

  • java.lang.Object
    • todomato.Task

  • public class Task
extends java.lang.Object
    This class stores a Task description, and optional additional attributes. The attributes can be the following:
    • start time
    • end time
    • date
    • location

    A Task may be constructed with any subset of the possible additional information, as long as it has a description.
